# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# Format: <from>  <to>  <status>

# Retire the deleted dress-rehearsal client site. The page was removed from the
# repo, but Pages kept serving a stale copy of the directory URL (its own cache
# sets s-maxage=604800, so a zone purge does not clear it). This rule takes
# priority over the stale asset and sends visitors to the homepage. Safe to
# delete once the cache has aged out.
/clients/the-smith-family/*  /  301
